Zevi Wolmark https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zevi_Wolmark 0 Zevi Wolmark (born August 19, 1962) is an American film and theatre actor and artist. His on-screen career was at its peak in the late 1980s and early 1990s. He is chiefly known for his appearance in the 1988 TV Series Superboy as well as for lending his voice to the animated TV Series C.O.P.S.
